{"tid":1814182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行集會 歌單","createTime":"2020-01-06T21:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T21:19:14.000Z","uid":317277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f002d8edf50f4af54bc27a05af8eda9a2c27f2","tid":1814182,"uid":317277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:13:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">榮光</span></span>其實一定係最廣泛認識 我都認同佢帶動到好多士氣 但係個人認為係感動偏多 聽完唔會想<span style=\"color: red;\">硬碰硬</span> 刺激唔到和理非同埋廣大市民進化 反而變左安撫心靈 延續和理非戰線<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 一啲可以提升士氣既歌 例如之前巴打講既不屈進行曲 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋Rap</span></span> 都可以大大提升士氣 但係一啲直接屌柒政府黑警就避免播 始終有部分人仲有潔癖 同埋黑警又有機會話煽動仇恨情緒而停止活動<br />\n<br />\n以下係一啲我認為可以提升士氣既歌：<br />\n<br />\n呢首講出前線心聲 有類似和理非質疑點解勇武要硬碰硬既對白 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6j05Nno2scc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6j05Nno2scc&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=d59eb785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6j05Nno2scc</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">你怕 我同你一樣都怕<br />\n怕痛 怕子彈 怕比人虐打<br />\n怕比人打壓 怕比人射殺<br />\n怕被囚禁入臭格 一樣怕被還柙<br />\n呢個地方奴隸思想植根 自由唔值得年輕人犧牲<br />\n但係我地就係太天真<br />\n發夢 只係因為良心</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0YhtHt-8FBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0YhtHt-8FBY&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=e4987e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0YhtHt-8FBY</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">你聽得到我們呼叫嗎<br />\n為了以後 萬百天後<br />\n活在真正自由<br />\n<br />\n你聽得到我們掙扎嗎<br />\n為了自由 為了自由<br />\n我們不會退後</span></div><br />\n<br />\n呢首唔洗多講 但始終有少少粗口 可能有家長唔鍾意<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0UWKctPom6A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0UWKctPom6A&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=7416cc78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0UWKctPom6A</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首係我覺得最正既一首 無論詞 音樂定MV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZQGR-RvFONw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZQGR-RvFONw&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=6ebc4ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZQGR-RvFONw</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首啲詞都好中 但好多粗口<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4S_9Eckpcwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4S_9Eckpcwg&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=2fbd6bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4S_9Eckpcwg</a><br />\n<br />\n我地要啲士氣令到大家肯踏前一步而唔係keep住有事就後退屌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以再咁畏縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6baa1acc39297a297dd4fd048ee80e81d81f2e0","tid":1814182,"uid":317277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f002d8edf50f4af54bc27a05af8eda9a2c27f2","tid":1814182,"uid":317277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:13:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">榮光</span></span>其實一定係最廣泛認識 我都認同佢帶動到好多士氣 但係個人認為係感動偏多 聽完唔會想<span style=\"color: red;\">硬碰硬</span> 刺激唔到和理非同埋廣大市民進化 反而變左安撫心靈 延續和理非戰線<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 一啲可以提升士氣既歌 例如之前巴打講既不屈進行曲 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋Rap</span></span> 都可以大大提升士氣 但係一啲直接屌柒政府黑警就避免播 始終有部分人仲有潔癖 同埋黑警又有機會話煽動仇恨情緒而停止活動<br />\n<br />\n以下係一啲我認為可以提升士氣既歌：<br />\n<br />\n呢首講出前線心聲 有類似和理非質疑點解勇武要硬碰硬既對白 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6j05Nno2scc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6j05Nno2scc&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=d59eb785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6j05Nno2scc</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">你怕 我同你一樣都怕<br />\n怕痛 怕子彈 怕比人虐打<br />\n怕比人打壓 怕比人射殺<b